	   <tr><td colspan=2>My weapons skils are still the same from lvl 15, Heck im lvl 31 now, If you truely are a good cleric you shouldn't even use a weapon passed 15, i didn't. Just make sure your not in a dumb group who doesnt listen to destress calls and you will be ok. Remember we are casters not warriors, We dont fight!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
