	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hell levels are level 30, 35, 40, 45, and 50 on up.<br><br>They require anywhere from twice to three times the exp to level than other levels.&nbsp;&nbsp;They are indeed...hell.<br><br>I never carried a screaming mace, but I had mostly given up melee by level 25 or so.  Just jumped in and pounded on mobs when I was full mana to keep my 1hb and offense up.  I also let some low level mobs beat on me to keep defense and dodge up.  This will be very important at later levels, especially with the new heal aggro.  You will get beat on.<br><br>As I am a dwarf, I can't really answer your questions on weight problems.  My base str is 105, 126 with the gear I am wearing now.<br><br>However, maybe as you level you can find some gear that gives str as well as wis, like the ruby veil line of jewelry and such.  It helps somewhat.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
