	   <tr><td colspan=2>Depends on your level. Until level 30 you're better off going Moonstone than silver/jasper. If you go plat jasper at level 15 though it's better than the moonstone. At level 39 I had over 1.5K wis with a nearly 200 wis. You might try the mana calculator at eq.castersrealm.com to find out how much mana is generated by one point of wisdom at your level and plan your equipment accordingly.<br>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10116 target=_new> Baron Chakfor Shalebreak</a><br>High Priest of Xegony</td></tr>
