	   <tr><td colspan=2>LOL u want money really fast. Well what i did is i went to EC. You go in side the EC tunnel there must be 100 ppl in there. Go up to ppl and ask them if u can have their spare Silver and Copper. After a while u will have soem money. Go to the Bank in East Freeport and exchnage the silver and copper for the higher lvl money like gold and Platinum. It worked for me. I gained about 50pp after a long time. Okay so this doesnt get u filthy rich but u get some money to buy stuff. When u get high lvl i found that the best loot i got was from Lake Rathe right next to the South Karana zone. Make sure ur at least lvl 17 or so. Good luck.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
