	   <tr><td colspan=2>Belt of the Cenobite drops off a triggered spawn in Fronteer Mountains.&nbsp;&nbsp;He is one of the Fronteer Mountains Cycle spawns.  Start in the South East Corner and kill "A Goblin Raider" then go from there.  Best spoiler is on EQ Druids to give a very detailed guide to running the cycle.<br><br>Bring big friends, we had deaths doing this cycle with a group of 4 lvl's 44 - 49.  Lots of blue agro's still (even at level 49) in the areas you need to kill the named stuff.<br>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 60 DE Gravelord</td></tr>
