	   <tr><td colspan=2>basically, the way to keep your defense skill maxed out for each level is to pull the lowest level mobs you can find that still con blue to you.&nbsp;&nbsp;let them beat on you, root them, back up heal yourself, walk back into their range, repeat til your defense is maxed for your level.<br><br>please make sure you do this next to a zone so you can run away if you have to.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
